rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm always just cutting down trees here, so I'm
a bit out of touch with the world.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But the craftsmen in Torigo use the wood from here
to make wonderful furniture and instruments...

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0003
rows.name: And the customers are happy to use them...

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0005
rows.name:
That's why, no matter what happens, I think
I'll just keep cutting down trees here every day.
